abstract: James R Oestreich reviews performance by the Minnesota Orchestra, conducted by Osmo Vanska, at Carnegie Hall.
snippet: The Finnish music director Osmo Vanska led the Minnesota Orchestra in Tchaikovsky and Nielsen at Carnegie Hall on Thursday.
lead_paragraph: The Finnish music director Osmo Vanska led the Minnesota Orchestra in Tchaikovsky and Nielsen at Carnegie Hall on Thursday.
